            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/airpods-max-usb/mobile-music/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 12:28:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1302031</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 为 AirPods Max 推出了韧体更新，提供了两个重要的功能升级：无损音讯（Lossless Audio）与超低延迟音讯（Low Latency Audio）。在新升级中，用家只要以 USB-C 线连接你的耳机与 iPhone／iPad／Mac 电脑，就可以直接以有线方式传输高频宽的无损压缩音乐，从而提升音乐细致度。另一方面也解决了过去在打机、直播或剪片过程中的音讯延迟问题。以下我们就 USB 连接后的音质表现进行实测，并探讨其实际效果。（留意更新只支援 USB-C 版本的 AirPods Max 耳机，Lightning 版本的耳机暂未支援）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1.jpg 598w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1302079 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1-338x580.jpg" alt="" width="338" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1-338x580.jpg 338w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1.jpg 524w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 338px" /></a></p><h2>韧体更新与操作方法</h2><p>为了启用这些新功能，使用者首先需要更新 AirPods Max 的韧体。操作步骤如下：</p><h2><b>Step 1</b></h2><p>更新你的<b> iPhone/iPad/Mac</b>：确保 iPhone 或 iPad 更新至 iOS 18.4 或 iPadOS 18.4，或是将 Mac 更新至 macOS Sequoia 15.4。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
